Muchidzidzo [[fundoyetsimba]], '''hutizapakati''' (centrifugal) zvinoreva kufamba ne[[rudzivo]] rwunobuda kunze rwuchitiza pakati. 

*Fosi yehudzivapakati (centripetal force) inokonzera kuti mutumbi ufambe nenzira ine kuumbwa kwemunyonga kana kuti denderedzwa. 

*[[Fosi yehutizapakati]] ifosi inoita makakatanwa neFosi yehudzivapakati. Apo Fosi yeHudzivapakati inenge iri kukakatira mukati kuti mutumbi urambe uri kufamba mu[[denderedzwa]], Fosi yehutizapakati inenge ichidhonzera kunze nokuda kwe ''inertia''.
